ESTATE OF Earnest Lee BOYLAND, et al., Petitioners,
v.
DEPARTMENT OF AGRICULTURE, et al. No. 19-636 Supreme Court of the United States. January 21, 2020 Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied. Justice Kavanaugh took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
